data.title: The Winter War
data.meta_description: 1939 Moscow lies saying it wants to protect itself from security threats inside Finland & invades it as part of a secret Russian Colonialism deal with Hitler to carve up Europe. Amid heavy losses the Kremlin settled for 11% of Finland. Over 400,000 were slaughtered.
data.text:
1939

Moscow lies saying it wants to protect itself from security threats inside Finland & invades it as part of a secret Russian Colonialism deal with Hitler to carve up Europe. Amid heavy losses the Kremlin settled for 11% of Finland. Over 400,000 were slaughtered.
